WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
A few days after the apple orchard incident

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
my mother's cousin, Miss Bray,

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
came to see us, bringing her daughter Lucy.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Their home had been in Mercer County, West Virginia,

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.000
but I had overheard my pa say

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.000
that Mr. Bray had a heavy case

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.000
of Western fever.